Pre-Game Insights: Iqraam Rayners will start against Algeria in a tightly contested international friendly.
Hlatshwayo still believes in his chances of being selected for the national team.
Broos has raised questions about the standard of the PSL compared to international level.
Evidence Makgopa impressed under Hugo Broos during the 2022 World Cup qualifiers and at the Africa Cup of Nations.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Rayners will have a stronger combination around him than the experimental XI used against Andorra.
